{"tid":1548450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［入機場］到底離島有咩玩？","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T07:09:49.000Z","uid":254330,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d1123fb4bad3f3e2fa20b59d5be166e1fc17a0","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:22:41.000Z","msg":"邊個話搭A/E車就一定去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">欣賞青馬大橋、去大澳買蝦醬、去大浪灣/貝澳游水、參觀石壁水塘、搭昂坪360、上鳳凰山<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n離島咁多野玩,邊個話一定要入機場wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旅遊業成日話市況幾差,依家係咪唔比去離島支持香港旅遊業先。<br />\n<br />\n利申 上述資料由Bady Kingdom提供，旨在促進香港本地旅遊業發展。"},{"pid":"f1cf04ed9a769f0b3afd003041f090746f1a6caf","tid":1548450,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"大浪灣係石澳果邊啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d492b548ee167bd3d65cfb3422652d6440e92639","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1cf04ed9a769f0b3afd003041f090746f1a6caf","tid":1548450,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"大浪灣係石澳果邊啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ls27hYi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLs27hYi.png&h=6e77346d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有2個 撞名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22530ea4fa13674dadf47ca57a0c21297bb3eb54","