arget=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a0221e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"15fb154091d2f3fbb0993b0be0397b1bece9dbf5","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"依家係咪唔比香港市民到大澳買蝦醬番屋企炒芥蘭先"},{"pid":"1d75d24b47bed18e388a15b5b38c1f5db809a126","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:31:20.000Z","msg":"搭A/E車到東涌再轉車去迪士尼又得唔得先,玩完迪士尼搭昂坪360又唔比?<br />\n<br />\n我想振興香港經濟咋"},{"pid":"89f6c3e42241a4754905c6c6db78b99ccdd87ec7","tid":1548450,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"行outlet"},{"pid":"5caffbb83afa1ad4b184624c0468c975df66fc9b","tid":1548450,"uid":275605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"入緊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青馬好多狗"},{"pid":"3a62e69cc726ad31891773ccb3766a217d346a47","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"棚屋是大澳漁村的標誌，也是香港最為獨特的景觀之一。大澳曾是香港的主要漁港和駐軍鄉鎮，也是百年來的漁鹽業重地。世代以來，大澳都是漁民蜑家人的聚居地，漁民認為在平實的土地上居住缺乏安全感，所以就在岸邊建造棚屋住下來。密密麻麻的棚屋、縱橫交錯的水道與橋樑，因而構成大澳現今的面貌。<br />\n<br />\n大澳的棚屋就建在漁村中間一條河道的兩旁。棚屋戶戶相連，部分通道更會穿過鄰居的客廳或廚房，造就了親近的鄰里關係。傳統棚屋依漁船的概念設計，棚頭是漁民日常作息的地方，棚尾則用來曬鹹魚、海帶等。遊大澳，您可以乘舢舨小艇在水道中穿梭，近距離欣賞棚屋；又或者在漁村裡走一圈，感受大澳的漁村風貌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">東方威尼斯</span></span>"},{"pid":"7452b28db4f2389c54da4169ffd0583da30d5c13","tid":1548450,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b96a6adb1dbc6e9e9f075f94b9305a0c177ccad7","tid":1548450,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f453745a3da95a8679250bbf9bede6b2205ad91","tid":1548450,"uid":83232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3c311f13ae312c95f0ed2f3b98943905339521","tid":1548450,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"去迪士尼玩"},{"pid":"60134d47258280ad2090f6777058b2e928685e3d","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"Please use English to talk with YiJinJai.<br />\nFor example, I just want to visit Tai O for sightseeing.I have rights to to there.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150205e41b474c8b4d6a7507924192e406a38ab5","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60134d47258280ad2090f6777058b2e928685e3d","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"Please use English to talk with YiJinJai.<br />\nFor example, I just want to visit Tai O for sightseeing.I have rights to to there.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"to <span style=\"color: red;\">go</span> there"},{"pid":"fde767d3f9f231d879df3d4e38fcad4afabce58e","tid":1548450,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b76ab33a67ba24be306e7d29d565f231ac325d6b","tid":1548450,"uid":254330,"like":0,"disl